Title: local: Wrong state in 'best' aggregation of clustered services
Level: 1
Component: checks
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
Version: 1.6.0p20
Date: 1609168942
Class: fix

For clustered 'local' checks' services the aggregation mode 'best'
returned the wrong state in certain situations.
Some service results have been discarded inadvertently, leading to
an overall state that was worse that desired.

